{"hash":"ccc1fdb6f2e137c3d58940c987b6e7692227e094","data":{"post":{"title":"linux alias","path":"/post/2019-06-11-alias/","date":"11. June 2019","timeToRead":1,"category":{"id":"linux","title":"linux","path":"/category/linux/"},"tags":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"bashrc쉘에-등록\"><a href=\"#bashrc%EC%89%98%EC%97%90-%EB%93%B1%EB%A1%9D\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>.bashrc쉘에 등록</h2>\n<p>alias는 터미널을 껐다가 키면 사라지는데 영구히 저장하고 싶다면 .bashrc쉘에 등록해줘야 한다.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-sh line-numbers bashrc쉘\"><code class=\"language-sh\"># home디렉토리의 .bashrc쉘 열기($HOME/.bashrc)\n# 난 root계정으로 실행했으므로\nvim /root/.bashrc\n\n# 빈 자리에다가 alias등록\nalias ll='ls -al'<span class=\"line-numbers-rows\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>참고 : <a href=\"https://movenpick.tistory.com/26\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://movenpick.tistory.com/26</a></p>\n<p>@TODO 사용자 계정으로도 만들어서 테스트해보자</p>\n"},"metadata":{"siteUrl":"http://localhost:8080","utterances":{"repo":"phoenix741/comments.myblog","issueTerm":"title","label":"discussion"}}},"context":{}}